            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "Why do we need to handle this? Please report it to ctags-lsp. The implementation does not comply with the specification. It should not return null here.\n\nhttps://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/specifications/lsp/3.17/specification/#completionList",
